@startuml AI助手服务类图

title AI助手服务类图 (AI Assistant Service Class Diagram)

' 设置样式
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor White
  ArrowColor Black
  BorderColor Black
}
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

' Flask应用层
package "Flask Application Layer" {
    class App {
        +talk(): Response
        +talkStream(): Response
        +register_to_nacos(): void
        -NACOS_SERVER_ADDR: String
        -SERVICE_NAME: String
        -INSTANCE_IP: String
        -INSTANCE_PORT: int
    }
    
    class Main {
        +ask_question_post(): Response
        +ask_get(): Response
    }
}

' AI连接器层
package "AI Connector Layer" {
    class AIConnector {
        -api_key: String
        -client: OpenAI
        -model: String
        +__init__()
        +talk(question: str): dict
        +talkStream(question: str): Generator
    }
}

' 问答引擎层
package "QA Engine Layer" {
    class QAEngine {
        +parse_question(question: str): dict
        +answer_question(question: str): str
        -MUSCLE_SYNONYMS: dict
        -EQUIPMENT_SYNONYMS: dict
        -DIFFICULTY_SYNONYMS: dict
    }
    
    class TransCode {
        +generate_report(): void
        -client: OpenAI
    }
}

' Neo4j驱动层
package "Neo4j Driver Layer" {
    class Neo4jConnection {
        -driver: GraphDatabase.driver
        +__init__(uri, user, password)
        +close(): void
        +query(query, parameters): list
    }
    
    class Neo4jConn {
        <<singleton>>
        -instance: Neo4jConnection
    }
}

' 外部服务
package "External Services" {
    class NacosClient {
        <<Service Registry>>
        +add_naming_instance(): void
        +send_heartbeat(): void
    }
    
    class OpenAIClient {
        <<AI API>>
        +chat.completions.create(): Completion
    }
    
    class Neo4jDatabase {
        <<Graph Database>>
        +session.run(): Result
    }
}

' 关系连接
App --> AIConnector : uses
App --> QAEngine : uses
App --> Neo4jConn : uses
App --> NacosClient : registers to

Main --> QAEngine : uses

AIConnector --> OpenAIClient : calls

QAEngine --> Neo4jConn : queries

Neo4jConn o-- Neo4jConnection : creates

Neo4jConnection --> Neo4jDatabase : connects to

TransCode --> OpenAIClient : calls

note right of App
  Flask应用作为入口
  提供REST API接口
  注册到Nacos服务发现
end note

note right of AIConnector
  封装AI模型调用
  支持流式和非流式响应
  处理思考过程和回答
end note

note right of QAEngine
  解析用户问题意图
  构建Cypher查询
  生成自然语言回答
end note

note right of Neo4jConnection
  管理Neo4j数据库连接
  执行图谱查询
  返回结构化数据
end note

@enduml